WEBVTT

00:03.000 --> 00:05.000
I'll get us somewhere better soon.

00:05.000 --> 00:06.000
I know it's a bit skanky.

00:06.000 --> 00:09.000
I quite like the idea
of living in a caravan.

00:09.000 --> 00:10.000
It's romantic.

00:12.000 --> 00:18.074
